    "home_faq": {
      "type": "faq-section",
      "blocks": {
        "faq_1": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How fast is delivery in Qatar?",
            "answer": "<p>Our own delivery fleet reaches most Qatar addresses in as fast as 3 hours from order confirmation, subject to product availability and your address. Where we use our courier partner, delivery is typically 6 to 8 hours.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_2": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you ship outside Qatar?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. We ship to more than 40 countries across the GCC, the wider Middle East, Asia, Europe and North America. GCC orders typically arrive in 2 to 4 business days, and other destinations in 7 to 10 business days including handling. You will see whether we ship to your country at checkout.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_3": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Are your products genuine?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. Lighting Souq is an authorised reseller and distributor of established lighting brands including Philips, OSRAM and LEDVANCE, and we hold direct distributor or dealership agreements with select manufacturers. Every product we list is sourced through authorised channels, and we are certified under Qatar's Theqa program.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_4": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Which lighting brands do you stock?",
            "answer": "<p>We stock over 50 brands. That includes Osram, Philips, LEDVANCE, GE, Sylvania, Tungsram, Kosnic and Bell Lighting in lighting; Xiaomi, Philips Hue, Yeelight, Sonoff, Amazon and Google in smart home; KDK and Panasonic in fans; and Vettam, Wink and Glint, which are manufactured to our specifications and sold exclusively through Lighting Souq.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_5": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What payment methods do you accept?",
            "answer": "<p>We accept Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Apple Pay, Google Pay and regional debit cards including NAPS and KNET through MyFatoorah, plus PayPal, Telr and Pay Later installment options where available.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_6": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you supply lighting for projects and bulk orders?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. We supply homes, offices, hospitality venues and businesses across Qatar and the wider region. Send your list through the bulk orders page and our team will return project pricing and stock availability.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
